WaarpSnmp 1.1.3 API Reference

The Waarp SNMP project contains the utility classes to implement SNMP support (agent) in Waarp other projects (as Waarp Gateway FTP or Waarp OpenR66).

See:
          Description


Waarp SNMP Support package
org.waarp.snmp Classes implementing Main functionalities to be used by Goldengate Projects
org.waarp.snmp.interf Interfaces to be implemented by Goldengate Projects
org.waarp.snmp.r66 Base class for OpenR66 MIB implementation to be used by OpenR66 Project
org.waarp.snmp.utils Utility Classes used by SNMP support

 

The Waarp SNMP project contains the utility classes to implement SNMP support (agent) in Waarp other projects (as Waarp Gateway FTP or Waarp OpenR66). It is based on the project SNMP4J.
